WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:10.182 --> 00:00:14.965
Double tap the "Home" button to bring down the notification tray, tap the "Settings" icon

00:00:14.966 --> 00:00:18.628
Tap "Personalization"

00:00:18.628 --> 00:00:21.848
Tap "Quick settings"

00:00:21.848 --> 00:00:25.608
Scroll down and tap the checkbox beside "Wi-Fi hotspot"

00:00:25.608 --> 00:00:30.246
Maximum number is ten toggles,
disable one of the toggle and enable "Wi-Fi hotspot" toggle

00:00:30.246 --> 00:00:35.121
Swipe down from notification bar, the toggle is added

00:00:35.121 --> 00:00:37.431
Tap the "Wi-Fi hotspot" toggle to enable it

00:00:37.431 --> 00:00:39.899
Tap "OK" to confirm

00:00:44.646 --> 00:00:48.326
Double tap the "Home" button to bring down the notification tray

00:00:48.326 --> 00:00:56.662
Tap the "Wi-Fi hotspot" toggle to disable it

00:00:58.069 --> 00:01:02.292
Double tap the "Home" button to bring down the notification tray, tap the "Settings" icon

00:01:02.292 --> 00:01:05.085
Tap "More..."

00:01:05.085 --> 00:01:07.556
Tap "Tethering &amp; portable hotspot"

00:01:07.556 --> 00:01:12.531
Tap "Portable Wi-Fi hotspot" to enable the hotspot, tap "OK" to confirm

00:01:20.686 --> 00:01:22.990
Tap "Portable Wi-Fi hotspot settings"

00:01:22.990 --> 00:01:25.471
Tap "Configure Wi-Fi hotspot"

00:01:25.471 --> 00:01:31.470
You may change SSID, Security and Password here

00:01:41.134 --> 00:02:01.563
Tap "Discoverable" to make hotspot discoverable or not

00:02:01.563 --> 00:02:07.030
Tap "Power save" to disable hotspot automatically after 10 minutes of inactivity

00:02:07.030 --> 00:02:09.554
Back to "Tethering &amp; portable hotspot"

00:02:09.554 --> 00:02:14.630
Tap "Portable Wi-Fi hotspot" again to disable the hotspot

